{"tid":2278383,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"傷殘車長期霸佔錶位","createTime":"2020-11-09T06:20:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T12:43:36.000Z","uid":227419,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bfa8822e22903a33940053536b1c011bba61cc28","tid":2278383,"uid":227419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T06:20:32.000Z","msg":"傷殘車泊錶位不嬲有特權，根據運輸處「持有傷殘人士泊車許可證的人士：1.可<span class=\"large\">豁免收費</span>使用設有<span class=\"large\">收費錶</span>的路旁泊車位；2.可使用傷殘人士專用泊車位；及3.可以<span class=\"large\">半價</span>使用任何運輸署轄下<span class=\"large\">政府多層停車場</span>的特定停車位。」<br />\n<br />\n之但係唔少地方嘅咪錶位都俾依班傷殘車主當停車場咁長期停泊，車都無郁過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搞到真正有需要使用嘅車主無得泊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可悲嘅係我地嘅正苦同popo從來都唔會理停泊多於24小時嘅車輛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />抄牌點抄得勁都唔關班「傷殘車主」事"},{"pid":"96bcc558ad189fe87c3b7520b30899aa321e2ac1","tid":2278383,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T06:26:42.000Z","msg":"你搞到自己變傷殘人士咪得囉"},{"pid":"327e70ccf7f0f7f456d04535b2c332563d2ddd1f","tid":2278383,"uid":94501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96bcc558ad189fe87c3b7520b30899aa321e2ac1","tid":2278383,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T06:26:42.000Z","msg":"你搞到自己變傷殘人士咪得囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T06:28:58.000Z","msg":"唔洗搞 已經係腦殘"},{"pid":"8f86ed77de354c3ba32ba2e3d40da9ec1c873fe6","tid":2278383,"uid":10593,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T12:43:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}